Package: sec.gov
Title: SEC EDGAR Client for R
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: A self-contained client for the SEC EDGAR system. Provides
    entity resolution, company filings, XBRL facts, bulk datasets, and
    S3-based filing parsers (XBRL, segments, ownership, holdings,
    tables, subsidiaries, text, Excel, HTML). All public functions
    return tibbles with proper types. No database dependencies.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports: dplyr, httr2, jsonlite, tibble, tidyr, xml2
Suggests: readxl
NeedsCompilation: no
